  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink250-kilavi">talaimakaṭku vanta nōy murukaṉāl vantamai yikkaḻaṅku kūṟiṟṟ eṉṟu vēlaṉ coṉṉāṉ eṉpatu kēṭṭa tōḻi yakkaḻaṅkiṟk uraippāḷāyc cevili kēṭkumāṟṟāl aṟattoṭu nilai kuṟittuc colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">What the friend, standing [in accordance] with duty, said as one who spoke to the Molucca-bean by the way of foster-mother listening; [the friend who]
          listened to the Vēlaṉ who said that this Molucca-bean declared the pain that had
          befallen the heroine to have come about by Murukaṉ. 
    
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink250">
          <l>poypaṭu paṟiyāk kaḻaṅkē meyyē</l>
          <l>maṇivaraik kaṭci maṭamayi lālu nam</l>
          <l>malarnta vaḷḷiyaṅ kāṉaṅ kiḻavō</l>
          <l>ṉāṇṭakai viṟalvē ḷallaṉivaḷ</l>
          <l>pūṇṭāṅ kiḷamulai yaṇaṅki yōṉē</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l>O Molucca bean, unaware of the occurrence of falsehood,</l>
          <l>the truth, in fact, is this:</l>

          <l rend="space">he who tormented her ornament-bearing young breasts—</l>
          <l>our lord of the woodland with bloomed creepers,</l>
          <l>where naïve peacocks dance</l>
          <l>in the forests of sapphire mountains—</l>

          <l rend="space">is not the victorious Vēḷ worthy of manhood.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
